{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_52_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 暇だから行きますけど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\n突然呼び出してなんの用ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nWhy did you call me out here all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "「暇だ」って突然送ってきたのは怜の方じゃないか\nどうしたんだ？　旅行で暇だなんて聞いたことないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the one who suddenly texted “I’m bored‚” remember?\nWhat’s wrong? I’ve never heard of someone being bored on a trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4851244609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。そういえばさっき送ったんでした\n旅行って何をしたらいいか分からなくて、つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. I guess I did send that earlier.\nI just… don’t really know what you’re supposed to do on a trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4851246516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　美味しいご飯を食べたり、普段は\n見られない景色を見たり……いくらでもあるだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? You can eat good food‚ see sights\nyou normally wouldn’t… there’s plenty to do‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3041953723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "私も調べたんですけどいまいち楽しみ方が分からなくて\n家族旅行にもあまり行く機会がなかったですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did look things up‚ but I still couldn’t quite figure out how to enjoy it.\nI didn’t really get many chances to go on family trips either…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8645351727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5564400673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……そうか、怜は少し前まで家族の仲が……俺は）\n（マネージャー失格だ。早く気付いてあげるべきだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I see. Rei’s family situation used to be…）\n（I’m a failure as a manager. I should’ve realized sooner.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.080748272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。暇なら、少し俺に任せてくれないか？\n怜に旅行の楽しさを教えてみせるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. If you’re bored‚ why not leave it to me for a bit?\nI’ll show you how fun traveling can be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.8738999685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "え、突然どうしたんですか……？\nなんか妙に意気込んでますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What’s gotten into you all of a sudden…?\nYou seem oddly fired up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2153284073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、せっかくの慰安旅行だ。怜にいい思い出を残して\nほしくてな。暇だからいいよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s a recreational trip. I want you to make good memories.\nSince you’re bored‚ it’s fine‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0719952267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきから暇、暇って……暇人扱いされるのは\nなんか嫌です！　暇だから行きますけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You keep saying “bored‚ bored”… I don’t like being treated\nlike I have nothing better to do! I’ll go because I’m bored‚ though!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3932877541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2173692069
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2173692069
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-snow-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 86.0266210874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり北海道といえば食べ歩きだろう\n海の幸から珍味まで沢山あるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to Hokkaido‚ food hopping is a must.\nFrom fresh seafood to rare delicacies‚ there’s tons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.366195794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、お店だけじゃなくて屋台も一杯出ていますね\nお祭りみたいで賑やかです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true—there aren’t just restaurants‚ but lots of food stalls too.\nIt feels lively‚ almost like a festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0778683345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.3902501425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ホタテに牡蠣、海鮮丼……あ、アイスもあるぞ\nどうだ？　一つと言わず、二つ、三つでもいいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look—scallops‚ oysters‚ seafood bowls… oh‚ there’s ice cream too.\nHow about it? Not just one—two or three is fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや……そんなに食べられませんよ\n私を太らせたいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no… I can’t eat that much.\nAre you trying to make me gain weight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4529707592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0211342496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳じゃないが、食べ歩きに遠慮は厳禁だからな\n食べたい物があったらすぐに言うんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all‚ but holding back defeats the purpose of food hopping.\nIf there’s something you want‚ just say it right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.8090954147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……なんか、今日は圧が凄いですね\n遠慮はしてないので大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay… you’re really intense today.\nI’m not holding back‚ though‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.207598591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.955240536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの『蟹掴み取り』って書いてる屋台、人だかりが\n凄いですね。少し見てもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ that stall that says “Grab-a-Crab”…\nit’s really crowded. Can we take a look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.107598591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.9397823019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……本当に生きてる蟹を掴むんですね。あの大きな\nハサミに挟まれたらと思うと……ちょっと怖いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… you really grab a live crab.\nIf those big claws pinch you… that’s kind of scary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0742723784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "甲羅を掴めば挟まれることはないと思うぞ\nせっかくだし挑戦してみるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you grab the shell‚ it shouldn’t pinch you.\nSince we’re here‚ want to try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.2860179268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……やっぱりやめておきます\n目立ちそうだし、怖いし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… maybe I’ll pass.\nIt’ll draw attention‚ and it’s scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6071751278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "怜も気になってるんだろう？　旅行では普段やらない\nことも思い切って挑戦するのが思い出を作るコツだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re curious‚ aren’t you? On a trip‚\ntrying things you normally wouldn’t is how you make memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4333435059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.2472419424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "思い出を……わ、分かりました\nそこまで言うならやってみます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Memories… O-okay.\nIf you insist that much‚ I’ll try…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.6221859616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.0405753138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、蟹の背中……ここを掴めばいいんですよね？\nいきますよ……えいっ！　け、結構重い……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ the crab’s back… I grab it here‚ right?\nHere I go… hngh! I-it’s pretty heavy…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.1221859616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
